data.description: Welcome to this lovely 3 bed, 2 bath single family home located in the quaint and quiet Fosters Mill Rd in Boynton Beach.A lovely turnkey home that is ready for its new owners. Brand new 2023 roof assures for no needed work for new owners. Big back yard fully gated with white fencing and tankless water heater make this home lovely and easy to move into for its new owners.HOME IS BEING LISTED FOR RENT AS WELL AS SELL.
